    "It can not be '#{duplicate}'"

    "\e[31mSorry, that is an invalid answer. Please, try again.\e[0m"

    "#{name}, please enter a number (1-9) that is available to place an '#{symbol}'"

    "GAME OVER! #{player} is the winner!"

    "It's a draw"


